      "text": "### 2. `tests/scenario_framework/runner/main.ts`\n- If integration tests (`run-scenarios`) are executed within an environment carrying `EXA_BIN_PATH`, it avoids dropping to a default `shell` invocation of `\"exactl\"` which might mistakenly test the user's root development toolset.\n- It explicitly forces the step executor (`exactlExecutable`) to rely on `$EXA_BIN_PATH/exactl`, guaranteeing sandbox test hermeticity.",
